    "Id": "chassisdef_warlord_WAR-TT1",
    "Name": "Warlord",
    "Details": "The Warlord carries its main damage dealers on the right side of the 'Mech, a Gauss rifle in the arm and an ER PPC in the side torso. A center torso mounted ER Large Laser is able to provide extra damage at range as needed, but needs to be overused due to the limited cooling from the 'Mechs twelve double heat sinks. At closer ranges the 'Mech can switch to use its seven Medium Lasers, with an SRM-6 as an extra punch. The final weapon is an Artemis IV-enabled LRM-20, able to provide accurate missile fire at most ranges.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Energy</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.18</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_warhammer"
